Titolo: Asphalt Overdrive

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Asphalt Overdrive is a 2014 endless running video game published by Gameloft and developed by their Madrid studio. It is a spinoff of the Asphalt series and the eleventh title overall.  After a showcase in June 2014 at the E3 event, it was released in September 24, 2014 for iOS, Android and Windows Phone, Windows 8.1. The game is officially retired and no longer supported.
Overdrive marks a departure from previous games in the series, as it is an on-rails endless platformer in the vein of Temple Run and Subway Surfers, and takes place in a 1980s-style rendition of Southern California.

Genere: Endless runner

Valutazione: 59
